# HomeGuard Smart Security System - Component List

## 1. Microcontroller & Display
- Arduino Nano Board (1)
- 16x2 LCD Display (1)

## 2. Sensors
- Motion Sensor (PIR) (1)
- Small Limit Switch (2) - for gate & door
- Water Tank Sensor (Copper wire based) (1)
- Rain Sensor (Copper coil based) (1)
- Home AC Supply Sensor (Zener diode based) (1)
- LDR (Light Dependent Resistor) (1) - for fence light
- Voltage Sensor Module (1) - for voltage cutoff

## 3. Actuators & Control
- 12V DC Buzzer/Hooter (1)
- Red LED (10)
- Relay Module (2) - for water tank motor & voltage cutoff
- Water Pump/Motor (1)

## 4. Logic ICs
- IC 7432 (OR Gate) (2)
- IC 7408 (AND Gate) (1)
- IC 7474 (Flip-Flop) (1)

## 5. Power Components
- Transformer 12-0-12V 2A (1)
- Voltage Regulator 7805 (1)
- Voltage Regulator 7812 (1)
- Diode 1N4007 (3)

## 6. Passive Components
- Resistor 100Ω (10)
- Resistor 1KΩ (20)
- Capacitor 1000μF/25V (1)
- Capacitor 10μF/25V (2)
- Capacitor 0.1μF Disc (5)
- Transistor BC547 (7)

## 7. Switches & Wiring
- Push Switch (Red & Green) (1 each)
- Jumper Wires (Male-to-Female: 10, Male-to-Male: 10)
- Ribbon Wire 3m (10 colors) (1)
- General Purpose PCB 2m (1)
- Power Cable 2m (1)

## 8. System Architecture Components

### Input Layer:
- 7 Sensors (Motion, Gate, Door, Water, Rain, AC, Light)
- 2 Push Switches (Control & Reset)

### Processing Layer:
- OR Gate (Sensor signal aggregation)
- AND Gate (Alarm triggering logic)
- Flip-Flop (System state management)
- Arduino Nano (Data processing)

### Output Layer:
- Buzzer & LED (Alerts)
- 2 Relays (Motor control & Power cutoff)
- LCD Display (Status)
